---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { donationLinks, site } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Donate" description="Support development of Simple Text Editor.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">Donate</p>
      <h1>Support Simple Text Editor</h1>
      <p class="lead">Simple Text Editor is free, open source, and maintained in my spare time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p>
        A dedicated group of contributors helps translate the application. If you encounter errors,
        please report them on GitHub.
      </p>
      <p>If you wish to support the work, you can use one of these options:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Buy Me a Coffee:</strong> <a href={donationLinks.buyMeACoffee}>buymeacoffee.com/maxistar</a></li>
        <li><strong>PayPal:</strong> <a href={donationLinks.paypal}>paypal.me/maximstarikov</a></li>
        <li><strong>Bitcoin:</strong> <a href={`bitcoin:${donationLinks.bitcoin}`}>{donationLinks.bitcoin}</a></li>
        <li><strong>TON:</strong> <a href={`ton://transfer/${donationLinks.ton}`}>{donationLinks.ton}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Ethereum:</strong> <code>{donationLinks.ethereum}</code></li>
        <li><strong>USDT (TRC-20):</strong> <code>{donationLinks.usdtTrc20}</code></li>
      </ul>
      <p>Your support is a strong motivation to keep improving the application.</p>
      <p><a href={site.appStore.issues}>Report an issue on GitHub</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
